# Testing & Quality Assurance Guidelines

## Testing Strategy
Follow the comprehensive testing strategy outlined in [Implementation_Solution_Document.md](mdc:solution doc/Implementation_Solution_Document.md) and [Project_Implementation_Plan.md](mdc:solution doc/Project_Implementation_Plan.md).

## Testing Levels & Coverage

### Unit Testing (80%+ Coverage Required)
- **Java:** Use JUnit 5 with Mockito for mocking
- **Python:** Use PyTest with pytest-mock
- **TypeScript:** Use Jest with React Testing Library
- **Coverage Tools:** JaCoCo (Java), Coverage.py (Python), Jest (TypeScript)

### Integration Testing
- **API Testing:** Test all endpoints with Postman/Newman
- **Database Testing:** Test database operations and transactions
- **Service Testing:** Test service interactions and dependencies
- **External Integration:** Test third-party service integrations

### System Testing
- **End-to-End Testing:** Test complete user workflows
- **Cross-Browser Testing:** Ensure compatibility across browsers
- **Mobile Testing:** Test responsive design and mobile functionality
- **Performance Testing:** Load and stress testing with JMeter/K6

### Security Testing
- **OWASP Top 10:** Regular vulnerability assessments
- **Penetration Testing:** External security audits
- **Code Scanning:** Static and dynamic code analysis
- **Dependency Scanning:** Regular vulnerability scans

## Test Data Management
- **Synthetic Data:** Generate realistic test data
- **Data Isolation:** Separate test and production data
- **Data Refresh:** Regular updates to maintain relevance
- **PII Protection:** Never use real PII in tests

## Quality Gates
- **Code Review:** All code must pass peer review
- **Automated Testing:** All tests must pass in CI/CD pipeline
- **Performance Benchmarks:** Meet performance requirements
- **Security Compliance:** Pass security scans
- **Documentation:** Complete and up-to-date documentation

## Testing Tools & Infrastructure
- **Test Management:** Jira Test Management, TestRail
- **Automation:** Selenium, Cypress, custom frameworks
- **Performance:** JMeter, K6, custom performance tools
- **Security:** OWASP ZAP, SonarQube, manual testing
- **Monitoring:** Application performance monitoring tools

## Test Documentation
- **Test Plans:** Comprehensive test planning documents
- **Test Cases:** Detailed test case specifications
- **Test Results:** Document all test results and issues
- **Regression Testing:** Maintain regression test suites
- **User Acceptance:** Business stakeholder validation
